    @FunctionalInterface
public interface DoubleOperator2
extends OperatorN<java.lang.Double>, net.ashwork.functionality.primitive.doubles.ToDoubleFunctionN, net.ashwork.functionality.partial.Unboxed<Operator2<java.lang.Double>>, net.ashwork.functionality.partial.UnboxedInput<net.ashwork.functionality.primitive.doubles.ToDoubleFunction2<java.lang.Double,java.lang.Double>>, net.ashwork.functionality.partial.Variant<java.util.function.DoubleBinaryOperator>
    Represents an operation that accepts two double-valued operands and produces a result of the same type as its operands. This is the two-arity specialization of OperatorN. This is the double-consuming primitive specialization of ToDoubleFunction2.

    This is a functional interface whose functional method is applyAsDouble(double, double).
